window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Calamity James can see the dead, but that doesn’t mean she likes it.</b></p> <p>Calamity James, a reluctant paranormal detective, returns to her hometown for the first time in 10 years to attend her aunt’s funeral. When the local sheriff blackmails her into helping with a missing persons case, Cal can’t say no. Using her unique gift, sharp wits, and even sharper tongue, Cal flirts with death to solve the case.&nbsp;</p> <p>In Red River, the dead talk, and Cal is the only person who can hear them.</p>"; 
